data.description: $1000 back at closing (closing costs, buy down interest rate, etc.).   Come view this beautiful home on over half an acre in West Kyle!   Beautiful flooring, updated gorgeous kitchen with white, contemporary cabinets, and tons of natural light. 4 large bedrooms with loads of space.  Primary bedroom has an additional sitting area/office/flex room attached.  Covered back patio is amazing---outdoor ceiling fans and many beautiful trees and views.   Huge corner lot--with so much space and breathing room---roof was replaced in 2015.
